31312.text: [31312] StaticText 'MINI PORTABLE DESIGN - The TOZO PE1 portable speaker boasts a portable and mini design, with dimensions of 129*90*44 mm, even smaller than your palm. You can hang it on a backpack or slip it into your pocket for easy portability.'

31317.text: [31317] StaticText "MEMORY CLIMBING BUCKLE - With a redesigned carabiner that's integrated into the speaker itself for extra protection, take your TOZO PE1 anywhere and everywhere. Just clip on a belt, strap, or buckle and go explore the world."

31322.text: [31322] StaticText 'STABLE BLUETOOTH CONNECTION - Bluetooth 5.4 technology has a better and stable signal and high transmission rate ensure the reliability.Outstanding connection and built-in microphone for hands free calling mean more flexibility for you .'

31327.text: [31327] StaticText 'IPX8 WATERPROOF SHOWER SPEAKER - The TOZO PE1 Bluetooth speaker is not only thoroughly resistant to water, dust and sand, but aslo features IPX8 waterproof function, enabling it to withstand complete immersion in water up to one meter deep for 30 minutes without damage. Perfect for use in humid environments like bathrooms, swimming pools, and rain.'
